org.apache.flink.api.common.typeutils

类 CompatibilityResult<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.common.typeutils.CompatibilityResult<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - the type of the data being migrated.

    @PublicEvolving
public final class CompatibilityResult<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A CompatibilityResult contains information about whether or not data migration is required in order to continue using new serializers for previously serialized data.

    • 字段概要

        This is only relevant if migration is required.

      • compatible

        public static <T> CompatibilityResult<T> compatible()
        Returns a result that signals that the new serializer is compatible and no migration is required.
        返回:
        a result that signals migration is not required for the new serializer

      • requiresMigration

        public static <T> CompatibilityResult<T> requiresMigration(@Nonnull
                                                           TypeDeserializer<T> convertDeserializer)
        Returns a result that signals migration to be performed, and in the case that the preceding serializer cannot be found or restored to read the previous data during migration, a provided convert deserializer can be used.
        类型参数:
        T - the type of the data being migrated.
        参数:
        convertDeserializer - the convert deserializer to use, in the case that the preceding serializer cannot be found.
        返回:
        a result that signals migration is necessary, also providing a convert deserializer.

      • requiresMigration

        public static <T> CompatibilityResult<T> requiresMigration(@Nonnull
                                                           TypeSerializer<T> convertSerializer)
        Returns a result that signals migration to be performed, and in the case that the preceding serializer cannot be found or restored to read the previous data during migration, a provided convert serializer can be used. The provided serializer will only be used for deserialization.
        类型参数:
        T - the type of the data being migrated.
        参数:
        convertSerializer - the convert serializer to use, in the case that the preceding serializer cannot be found. The provided serializer will only be used for deserialization.
        返回:
        a result that signals migration is necessary, also providing a convert serializer.

      • requiresMigration

        public static <T> CompatibilityResult<T> requiresMigration()
        Returns a result that signals migration to be performed. The migration will fail if the preceding serializer for the previous data cannot be found.

        You can also provide a convert deserializer using requiresMigration(TypeDeserializer) or requiresMigration(TypeSerializer), which will be used as a fallback resort in such cases.

        返回:
        a result that signals migration is necessary, without providing a convert deserializer.
